{"tid":1874260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習落區罩不離口 京滬「半封城」","createTime":"2020-02-11T06:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T07:47:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"022786ce8fdefd0e307666e6bb62d6bb3e3dca49","tid":1874260,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200211/IU5XPRSMHKY5KVEKRF2UHK6W64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200211%2FIU5XPRSMHKY5KVEKRF2UHK6W64%2F&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yIVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=0b934763\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200211%2FIU5XPRSMHKY5KVEKRF2UHK6W64%2F&h=62d0abae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200211/IU5XPRSMHKY5KVEKRF2UHK6W64/</a><br />\n<br />\n習落區罩不離口 京滬「半封城」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國四大直轄市正式進入「半封城」狀態。武漢肺炎疫情持續擴散，繼天津及重慶後，北京及上海昨天亦相繼宣佈實行封閉式管理，嚴格監控各個小區人流進出。神隱多時的國家主席習近平，昨天終於戴上口罩現身，但只是在北京調研指導防疫工作，沒有仿效國務院總理李克強深入武漢疫區前線。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：逐家拍門通知 婆婆：唔知會點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200211/large/1581351919_3c34.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200211%2Flarge%2F1581351919_3c34.gif&h=8482f49b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平昨戴口罩到北京慰問居民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200211/large/1581351917_0bed.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200211%2Flarge%2F1581351917_0bed.gif&h=5c2a3e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山東部份企業復工，員工飯堂加設間隔。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200211/large/1581351918_8290.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200211%2Flarge%2F1581351918_8290.gif&h=3d87c348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疫情下居民避免接觸，用丫叉傳送貨物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n居滬港人︰𨋢有人唔會入<br />\n<br />\n習近平昨天在北京遠距離了解疫情防控工作，新華社指他下午前往朝陽區，先探熱，才進入安貞街道安華里社區，與居委會工作人員交流，又走到街頭慰問居民。習無論在室內與官員會面，或在戶外與巿民打招呼，一直戴上口罩，無響應特首林鄭月娥呼籲官員不應隨便戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n內地至今已有四省「封城」，80多個城市實施「封閉式管理」。昨天，首都北京及上海分別宣佈「半封城」，沒有明確工作或居所的人士將禁止進入上海。官方指目前上海大部份已實行封閉式管理，嚴控小區出入，外人進入必須登記及探熱，居民外出亦受管制等。實際上，有關措施由屋苑或物業管理公司自主執行，管制寬嚴不一，港人陳先生在上海工作，他接受本報訪問表示，所住屋苑一周前自發實施有限度出入，禁止外人入內，居民則可自由進入，不過他仍擔心受感染，已兩星期沒離開屋苑，僅到保安亭拿外賣，「落街都會避開人多出入嘅時間，𨋢有人唔會入」。"},{"pid":"d2ac5c22418f9b41cf29287c67dcaea551937cae","tid":1874260,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:07:37.000Z","msg":"【Twitter核爆料要人】美國參眾議員狂插中國軍方偷取美國國民資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1874234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1874234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">快啲大大力去淋火水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n入去<span style=\"color: gold;\">rt + like + reply</span>"},{"pid":"398b9a37444082ca1fee2b55fd93b8e852f24b9b","tid":1874260,"uid":158613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:15:09.000Z","msg":"香港政府：外面咩事都無"},{"pid":"0e6486cfb08db5ec13d3548f2744399b56055c39","tid":1874260,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:23:52.000Z","msg":"中國大陸四個直轄市歧視其他中國人，不合林鄭毒餓要求，"},{"pid":"d7bb9f07c228cbec72d9d8bf3579994922e95c56","tid":1874260,"uid":49359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:26:48.000Z","msg":"一蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cbde473b5ff0f78fe01824b30ea4aadf9d6da6","tid":1874260,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:28:48.000Z","msg":"一蘭飯盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b51eab668073a1bf24a2ebe50960e2216c9734","tid":1874260,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58ae3b9818e87d7ec7d1eea379d8478e1e3a5e4","tid":1874260,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"呢個習種係咪替身黎<br />\n隻眼唔似佢咁嘅"}]}